anyone else up there.

24:09.940 --> 24:12.773
- Are you not accustomed
to broken ponies in your stable?

24:12.810 --> 24:15.517
- You think Will Graham's
a broken pony?

24:15.550 --> 24:18.485
- I think you think Will is
a broken pony.

24:18.520 --> 24:20.147
Have you ever lost
a pony, Jack?

24:20.190 --> 24:22.750
- If you're asking me
whether or not I've ever

24:22.790 --> 24:25.884
