the answer is yes. Why?

24:25.930 --> 24:28.728
- I want to understand why
you're so delicate with Will.

24:28.760 --> 24:32.161
Because you don't trust him,
or because you're afraid
of losing another pony?

24:32.200 --> 24:36.034
- I've already had
my psych eval.

24:36.070 --> 24:38.868
- Not by me.

24:38.910 --> 24:42.107
You've already told me
about your mother.
Why stop there?

24:45.950 --> 24:49.579
- (laughing): Oh, great.
