take that personally, buddy.

25:29.360 --> 25:31.988
- Oh, I'm not recovering.
- Feed sugar to the fungus

25:32.030 --> 25:37.718
in your body, the fungus creates
alcohol, so it's like friends
helping friends, really.

25:37.770 --> 25:41.968
- It's not just alcoholics
who have compromised
endocrine systems.

25:42.000 --> 25:44.662
They all died of kidney failure?

25:44.710 --> 25:46.666
- Mm-hmm.

25:46.710 --> 25:48.701
- Death by diabetic
ketoacidosis.

25:48.740 --> 25:51.948
