28:00.840 --> 28:03.070
Special Agent Jack Crawford.
Which one of you is

28:03.110 --> 28:04.475
Eldon Stammets?

28:04.510 --> 28:06.478
- Eldon was just here.

28:06.510 --> 28:09.377
Just now.
- Is his car still

28:09.420 --> 28:12.241
