- Am I gonna wanna hear this?

29:00.470 --> 29:04.429
- No. And yes,
but mostly no.

29:08.210 --> 29:11.043
- Freddie Lounds.
- (Jack): TattleCrime.com.

29:11.080 --> 29:14.447
