41:36.190 --> 41:40.684
Did you really feel so bad
because killing him felt
so good?

41:42.700 --> 41:44.793
- I liked killing Hobbs.

41:49.070 --> 41:51.903
- Killing must feel good
to God too--

41:51.940 --> 41:54.306
he does it all the time.

41:54.340 --> 41:56.979
And are we not created
in his image?

41:57.010 --> 42:00.639
- That depends
who you ask.

42:00.680 --> 42:03.046
- God's terrific.

